The property is available to purchase individually or in a portfolio along with 2 Clarkshill Road, Secret Harbour located in Western Australia. Please request further details of Secret Harbour asset if of interest.

OVERVIEW

+ Passing income of $363,778p.a + GST

+ Highly exposed and trafficked location positioned next to Priceline Pharmacy, Woolworths and Bendigo Bank at the centre of Mildura

+ Anchored by highly regarded national GP and Allied Health provider Tristar Medical Group with 30 locations

+ Commercial 1 zoned landholding of 951sqm* across 2 (two) frontages

+ Modern and imposing improvements of 1,608sqm spread across two storeys

+ Favourable, long-term WALE of 6.4 Years + Options

+ Prominent street frontage with Langtree Avenue with ample on-street parking


LOCATION

+ Strategic regional investment location currently witnessing substantial regional migration from major metropolitan cities including Melbourne, Sydney and Adelaide

+Positioned in the centre of the Victoria, Adelaide and New South Wales Triangle and within the Sunraysia and Murray River region with a trade catchment of 60,000+ and growing

+ Mildura has a reputation for stylish shopping in a picturesque setting while it’s central business district (subject properties location) has more than 350 traders, including 300 specialty stores.
